com.alexgilleran.icesoap.envelope

Interface SOAPEnvelope

  • All Superinterfaces:
    XMLElement, XMLNode, XMLParentNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseSOAP11Envelope, BaseSOAP12Envelope, BaseSOAPEnvelope, PasswordSOAP11Envelope

    public interface SOAPEnvelope
extends XMLParentNode
    A representation of a SOAP envelope. Methods to retrieve the SOAP Header and Body tags are provided so that content can be added programatically.
    Author:
    Alex Gilleran
